Instant Messaging
-----------------

- Save chat sessions in history folder [DB]
- Add --auto-echo parameter to sip_im_session for automated tests [DB]
  When started with this option, the script automatically echos back all
  incomming messages, no user input is considered
- Add --auto-answer parameter to sip_im_session [DB]
  When started with this option, the script automatically accepts any
  incomming session without ringing.
- Reduce volume of IM related notifications to 50% [DB]
- Play a different sound for join/leave chat room [DB]
- Document MSRP client library usage, wiki page [DB]
- Port eventlet/greenlet to ARM [DB]
- MSRP focus [DB]
- MSRP multiparty chat [DB]
- Is-composing payload [DB]


